Global Decoking Valves Market Insights
Decoking Valves Market size was valued at USD 0.82 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.12 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Decoking Valves Market Overview
The global decoking valves market was valued at USD 1.3 billion in 2024 and is expected to reach USD 1.7 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2025 to 2030. The demand for decoking valves is driven by the increasing need for enhanced safety and operational efficiency in refinery and petrochemical industries. With advancements in valve technology, decoking valves are crucial in maintaining uninterrupted flow and reducing downtime during the coking process in refineries. This market is experiencing steady growth due to the rising adoption of automated systems in the refining process.

